window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Clark bought a discount catgirl at a pawnshop he knew they were supposed to do your dishes, clean your house, and cook your meals. He even knew they were supposed to fulfill your every desire.&nbsp;</p> <p>What he didn’t know was that once you have one, your life gets turned upside down especially because you can’t have just one.&nbsp;</p> <p>Please Note: This is a catgirl harem book where you can create your own catgirl to suit your every last whim while taking down an evil corporation.</p>"; 
